Chelsea is as good as having crashed out of the Champions League quarter final, being defeated 1-3 at home by Real Madrid on Wednesday. Chelsea conceded two quick goals in the first half, but scored one goal before the end of the half, ending the first half of the game 1-2.
The defending champion conceded another quick goal in the second half, trailing behind 1-3 to the end of the game.  live stream and score online, information, prediction,
The second leg of the quarter final will be played next Tuesday at the Santiago Bernabéu Real Madrid, Spain.
Chelsea will not be needing a miracle to defeat Real Madrid and qualify for the semifinal in the competition. The English club is not known for chanced games but known for a tradition of football. Chelsea would require to score three unreplied goals in Madrid to sail through to the next stage, otherwise, this is the end of the road for the club ion this year]s competition.
 
